<qti-assessment-item xmlns="http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0" xmlns:m="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance" identifier="Q39_v5" title="Q39_v5" time-dependent="false" adaptive="false" xsi:schemaLocation="http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0 https://purl.imsglobal.org/spec/qti/v3p0/schema/xsd/imsqti_asiv3p0_v1p0.xsd"><qti-response-declaration identifier="RESPONSE" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier"><qti-correct-response><qti-value>ChoiceB</qti-value></qti-correct-response></qti-response-declaration><qti-outcome-declaration identifier="SCORE" cardinality="single" base-type="float"><qti-default-value><qti-value>0</qti-value></qti-default-value></qti-outcome-declaration><qti-item-body><p>En un gimnasio se registró, para un mismo plan mensual, la siguiente información: Clases tomadas en el mes (x): 0, 1, 2. Monto total pagado (en pesos): 18000, 20500, 23000. Se sabe que el monto pagado corresponde a una tarifa fija de inscripción más un costo por cada clase tomada.</p><qti-choice-interaction response-identifier="RESPONSE" shuffle="false" max-choices="1"><qti-prompt>¿Cuál de las siguientes funciones <m:math><m:mi>G</m:mi><m:mo>(</m:mo><m:mi>x</m:mi><m:mo>)</m:mo></m:math> modela el monto mensual, en pesos, que debe pagar una persona que toma <m:math><m:mi>x</m:mi></m:math> clases en este plan?</qti-prompt><qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceA"><m:math><m:mi>G</m:mi><m:mo>(</m:mo><m:mi>x</m:mi><m:mo>)</m:mo><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>2500</m:mn><m:mi>x</m:mi></m:math></qti-simple-choice><qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceB"><m:math><m:mi>G</m:mi><m:mo>(</m:mo><m:mi>x</m:mi><m:mo>)</m:mo><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>2500</m:mn><m:mi>x</m:mi><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>18000</m:mn></m:math></qti-simple-choice><qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceC"><m:math><m:mi>G</m:mi><m:mo>(</m:mo><m:mi>x</m:mi><m:mo>)</m:mo><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mo>(</m:mo><m:mn>2500</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>18000</m:mn><m:mo>)</m:mo><m:mi>x</m:mi></m:math></qti-simple-choice><qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceD"><m:math><m:mi>G</m:mi><m:mo>(</m:mo><m:mi>x</m:mi><m:mo>)</m:mo><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>18000</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>2500</m:mn></m:math></qti-simple-choice></qti-choice-interaction></qti-item-body><qti-response-processing template="https://purl.imsglobal.org/spec/qti/v3p0/rptemplates/match_correct.xml" /></qti-assessment-item>